User Stories:
  I am Department Chair/Secretary 
    I want to enter TA PantherID and name when I hire them.
      So that the system knows they are employed?
    I can assign TAs to specific lab sections
      So that they work?
    I want to be able to remind TAs to enter their semester information
      So that I have updated information when scheduling.
  I am TA
    I need to register my information
      So the University knows of my employment as a TA
    I can update my information each semester
      So the system does not create schedule conflicts between work and class
    I can access my teaching schedule
      So I know when to teach
